tions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[4590,1420],"id":"9f76a1aa-30df-42a2-b2ad-17911fd41b4c","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hourly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — every 1 h. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Keep Valid Orders","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"a17a9d34-7db1-3a0a-554e-bb243d12df6d","name":"Note: Hourly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Keep Valid Orders\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Segment Audience","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"1c19f522-3cfe-506c-4e64-39f52a672641","name":"Note: Keep Valid Orders"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Segment Audience\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ ($json.score ?? 50) >= 50 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Step 1 — Welcome (Slack) · ②→ Tag for Slow Nurture","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"ca38f8a8-0418-b2da-bc43-9ef3cd5f9f9f","name":"Note: Segment Audience"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Step 1 — Welcome (Slack)\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Wait Before Step 2 · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,280],"id":"3a2140cb-2f97-d171-cd14-98ff2fbf616e","name":"Note: Step 1 — Welcome (Slack)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag for Slow Nurture\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,880],"id":"abe44dac-ad92-e52e-8b8b-e821e8bf1f41","name":"Note: Tag for Slow Nurture"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Wait Before Step 2\n\nPauses 3 days — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Converted Already?","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"b57419ea-2c1a-adef-a2be-442bb8b2e011","name":"Note: Wait Before Step 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Converted Already?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.status }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack) · ②→ Mark Converted — Stop Drip","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"07a7a3e8-66ce-d574-fd7f-cfc649025584","name":"Note: Converted Already?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack)\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Update Drip Status · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"801a4961-baf4-eb27-af85-b9b8cb17a1f8","name":"Note: Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Mark Converted — Stop Drip\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"0564f584-ea82-16d6-a90e-39c56dd28d79","name":"Note: Mark Converted — Stop Drip"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Update Drip Status\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Tag Pipeline Metadata · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"827df2ea-bf69-714e-c784-ee0d85ece03c","name":"Note: Update Drip Status"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"eb7d2d83-4747-cfff-e0a0-71d1559fb81a","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"f48029a7-f48e-93cf-c29f-11caf21ad7b6","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"be5b5c63-c193-3b33-d478-91bc7cbae133","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"93de04a0-85ed-cee3-f556-f662b7480520","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"5c9a4901-2d57-0572-669a-566fd90c1000","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"58c8f589-5def-0942-3889-9f4c430616e4","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"1decd1e2-7b23-597a-15fb-776537711e00","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,1540],"id":"76fbd039-bcae-f43b-e303-fa44b40b2428","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,1540],"id":"57bb1094-9aa3-1e69-d5c9-6d6522d4e00b","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Recover abandoned carts with HTTP / REST API and Microsoft Teams without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Abandoned Cart Recovery · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nRecover abandoned carts with HTTP / REST API and Microsoft Teams without manual work. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual cart recovery is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Keep Valid Orders → Segment Audience → Step 1 — Welcome (Slack) → Wait Before Step 2 → Converted Already? → Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack) → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to abandoned cart recovery without manual effort\n- Anyone automating cart recovery in e-commerce\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"6bf52f00-6cec-5b9b-311c-100d9f3219e5","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"05488981-8c40-fcd9-cf41-ff5bccea74f2","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"a7702af8-ae5c-863c-6510-a54092922bbf","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your cart recovery process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"ad4ab6ef-8433-80f9-ec10-50616be72cf1","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Hourly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Keep Valid Orders","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Keep Valid Orders":{"main":[[{"node":"Segment Audience","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Segment Audience":{"main":[[{"node":"Step 1 — Welcome (Slack)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Tag for Slow Nurture","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Step 1 — Welcome (Slack)":{"main":[[{"node":"Wait Before Step 2","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Wait Before Step 2":{"main":[[{"node":"Converted Already?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Converted Already?":{"main":[[{"node":"Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Mark Converted — Stop Drip","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Step 2 — Value Nudge (Slack)":{"main":[[{"node":"Update Drip Status","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Update Drip Status":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag for Slow Nurture":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Mark Converted — Stop Drip":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"4292bed6-cbbc-41ab-8794-12b27ca54029","id":"FDX09119"}